### HeyGen MCP Server — HTTP calls giống hệt Claude Code MCP
### Cần extension: humao.rest-client
###
### MCP = JSON-RPC 2.0 over HTTP, auth bằng OAuth 2.0 Bearer token
### Server: https://mcp.heygen.com/mcp/v1/
###
### LUỒNG DÙNG:
### 1. Chạy 3 request OAuth (block 1→2→3) để lấy access_token
### 2. Paste token vào @accessToken
### 3. Gọi MCP tools bằng JSON-RPC (block 4 trở đi)

@mcpUrl = https://mcp.heygen.com/mcp/v1/
@authBase = https://mcp.heygen.com

# Sau khi chạy OAuth flow, paste access_token vào đây:
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### ============================================================
### OAUTH 2.0 FLOW (chạy 1 lần, token thường sống nhiều giờ)
### ============================================================

### 0. Discover OAuth endpoints
GET {{authBase}}/.well-known/oauth-authorization-server


### 1. Dynamic client registration (MCP standard)
# @name register
POST {{authBase}}/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client_name": "REST Client Test",
  "redirect_uris": ["http://localhost:3000/callback"],
  "grant_types": ["authorization_code", "refresh_token"],
  "response_types": ["code"],
  "token_endpoint_auth_method": "none"
}

###
# Sau khi register xong, copy client_id:
# @client_id = {{register.response.body.client_id}}


### 2. Mở URL này trên browser để login HeyGen → nhận redirect
###    http://localhost:3000/callback?code=XXX&state=...
###    → copy code từ URL callback
###
###  Thay CLIENT_ID_FROM_STEP_1 vào URL dưới rồi paste vào trình duyệt:
###
###  https://mcp.heygen.com/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=CLIENT_ID_FROM_STEP_1&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback&state=test123&code_challenge_method=S256&code_challenge=E9Melhoa2OwvFrEMTJguCHaoeK1t8URWbuGJSstw-cM


### 3. Exchange code → access_token
###    (code_verifier phải match code_challenge ở bước 2)
###    Demo challenge trên dùng verifier: dBjftJeZ4CVP-mB92K27uhbUJU1p1r_wW1gFWFOEjXk
POST {{authBase}}/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=authorization_code
&code=PASTE_CODE_FROM_CALLBACK_URL
&redirect_uri=http://localhost:3000/callback
&client_id=PASTE_CLIENT_ID
&code_verifier=dBjftJeZ4CVP-mB92K27uhbUJU1p1r_wW1gFWFOEjXk


### ============================================================
### MCP PROTOCOL — JSON-RPC 2.0 calls
### ============================================================

### 4. Initialize MCP session
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 1,
  "method": "initialize",
  "params": {
    "protocolVersion": "2024-11-05",
    "capabilities": {},
    "clientInfo": { "name": "rest-client-test", "version": "1.0" }
  }
}


### 5. List all available tools (xem HeyGen MCP có tool gì)
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 2,
  "method": "tools/list"
}


### ============================================================
### 6. Call tool — LIST VIDEOS
### ============================================================
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 10,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "list_videos",
    "arguments": { "limit": 10 }
  }
}


### 7. Call tool — GET CURRENT USER
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 11,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_current_user",
    "arguments": {}
  }
}


### 8. Call tool — LIST AVATAR LOOKS
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 12,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "list_avatar_looks",
    "arguments": { "limit": 20 }
  }
}


### 9. Call tool — LIST VOICES
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 13,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "list_voices",
    "arguments": { "type": "public", "limit": 20 }
  }
}


### 10. Call tool — GET VIDEO STATUS
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 14,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "get_video",
    "arguments": { "videoId": "REPLACE_VIDEO_ID" }
  }
}


### 11. Call tool — CREATE VIDEO FROM AVATAR
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 15,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "create_video_from_avatar",
    "arguments": {
      "avatarId": "REPLACE_AVATAR_ID",
      "script": "Xin chào, đây là video test qua MCP.",
      "voiceId": "REPLACE_VOICE_ID",
      "aspectRatio": "9:16"
    }
  }
}


### 12. Call tool — CREATE SPEECH (TTS)
POST {{mcpUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json, text/event-stream

{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "id": 16,
  "method": "tools/call",
  "params": {
    "name": "create_speech",
    "arguments": {
      "text": "Đây là audio test qua MCP server.",
      "voiceId": "REPLACE_VOICE_ID",
      "speed": 1.0
    }
  }
}
